Class HtmlElement<T extends com.k2.XMLBuilder.XMLElement>

    T - The final class of the HtmlElement
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HtmlArea, HtmlBr, HtmlCol, HtmlColGroup, HtmlCommonPhrasingElement, HtmlCommonPhrasingElementNoTime, HtmlDl, HtmlEmbed, HtmlHr, HtmlIFrame, HtmlImg, HtmlInput, HtmlMeta, HtmlNoScript, HtmlOl, HtmlOptGroup, HtmlOption, HtmlParam, HtmlPicture, HtmlScript, HtmlSelect, HtmlSource, HtmlStyle, HtmlTable, HtmlTBody, HtmlTextArea, HtmlTFoot, HtmlTHead, HtmlTitle, HtmlTr, HtmlTrack, HtmlUl, HtmlWbr

    public abstract class HtmlElement<T extends com.k2.XMLBuilder.XMLElement>
extends HtmlGlobalElement<T>
    This abstract class is the base class for most HtmlElements. It defines the event attributes that are applicable to most html elements
    Author:
    simon
